metadata.name: A Memory Of Twinlakes
metadata.description:
A stunning view of a luxurious hotel beside Taal lake where the famous active volcano sits. It is a natural paradise with a majestic view. One of the best places to go to relax and admire the beauty of Twinlakes.

Artist Name: Kevin Icabales

Edition: 1/1

Size: 5760 x 3840
